quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  27,45,"“Ndipo ndithu Asamudu tidawatumizira m’bale wawo Swalih kuti awauze: “Mpembedzeni Allah.” Choncho adali magulu awiri omwe amakangana. (Ena adam’tsata pomwe ena adam’kana)"
  27,46,"“(Swaleh) adati: “E inu anthu anga chifukwa ninji inu mukufulumizitsa choipa (kuti chidze) musanachite chabwino? Bwanji simukupempha chikhululuko kwa Allah kuti muchitiridwe chifundo?”"
  27,47,"“(Iwo) adati: “Tapeza masoka oipa chifukwa cha iwe ndi omwe uli nawo.” (Iye) adati: “Tsoka lanu lili kwa Allah (chifukwa cha zolakwa zanu); koma inu ndinu anthu amene mukuyesedwa (ndi Allah kuti aone ngati mutsatire Mtumiki Wake kapena simutsatira).”"
  27,48,"“Ndipo m’mudzimo adalipo anthu asanu ndi anayi omwe amaononga pa dziko, ndipo samakonza (chilichonse koma kuchiononga)"
  27,49,"“(Iwo) adati: “Aliyense wa ife alumbire kwa Allah (kuti) iye (Swaleh) ndi banja lake timthira nkhondo usiku, ndipo kenako Timuuza mlowam’malo wake (kuti): “Sitidaone kuonongeka kwa m’bale wake; ndithu ife tikunena zoona.”"
  27,50,"“Ndipo adakonza chiwembu ndi kutchera misampha yamphamvu, nafenso tidawatchera misampha yowaononga, iwo asakudziwa"
  27,51,"“Tsono tayang’ana, kodi malekezero a chiwembu chawo adali otani! Tidawaononga iwo ndi anthu awo onse"
  27,52,“Izo ndinyumba zawo (zomwe zasanduka) mabwinja chifukwa cha chinyengo chawo. Ndithu m’zimenezo muli phunziro kwa odziwa
  27,53,“Ndipo tidawapulumutsa amene adakhulupirira pakuti amamuopa (Allah)
  27,54,"“Ndipo (akumbutse nkhani ya) Luti pamene adanena kwa anthu ake: “Kodi mukuchita zadama uku inu mukuziona?”"
  27,55,““Kodi inu mukugona ndi amuna pokwaniritsa chilakolako (cha chilengedwe) kusiya akazi? koma inu ndinu mbuli.”